{"tid":30063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[耶撚］所多瑪/蛾摩拉 OR支那 邊個邪惡d?","createTime":"2016-12-09T03:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T01:05:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e461361fc1edc29b0e31d8ddebd5f6e4d257139","tid":30063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"上帝點解唔毀滅支那？"},{"pid":"e9e31bbcb138674ff46d2c87807840d73270eec5","tid":30063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"所多瑪/娥摩拉，我睇唔到佢地有乜邪惡，但上帝又毀滅佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfece9bade5765b0c7d06d4cebd3adf9ed1b94f","tid":30063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"49bbfc16fad1c3473486674aa3f3e5f3c3f829ed","tid":30063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a20f5120fbf521b5f8cdcfe79f5501c821c586a2","tid":30063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54131fe99531d86016c434f0af214156786968b","tid":30063,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"祝上帝身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4af71bc8612589db12f3e0173a0d3441c365c7","tid":30063,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所多瑪/娥摩拉，我睇唔到佢地有乜邪惡，但上帝又毀滅佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係搞同性戀"},{"pid":"56c5c6cefb7371cabaf870129884e4bc358d57d6","tid":30063,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上帝點解唔毀滅支那？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為清狗搞緊君主立憲<br />\n但耶人孫中山不斷指揮炸彈襲擊<br />\n終於搞死清狗<br />\n跟住耶人孫中山又反對聯省自治<br />\n係都要打內戰<br />\n又採取聯俄容共政策 坐大共產黨<br />\n之後既耶人蔣介石又拒絕投降日本<br />\n終於孕育出支那國<br />\n所以一切都是神的安排"},{"pid":"ab65f5803e3cd5c50068a92571b6d244ddbe16bf","tid":30063,"uid":60612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"爆多芝士呀！係咪好邪惡呢"},{"pid":"e92414942cd9f41089204b4d585737faace4f385","tid":30063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:37:51.000Z","msg":"『索多瑪人在耶和華面前罪大惡極』（創13：13）<br />\n<br />\n『他們行姦淫，做事虛妄，又堅固惡人的手，甚至無人回頭離開他的惡。他們在我面前都像索多瑪；耶路撒冷的居民都像蛾摩拉。』（耶23：14）"},{"pid":"4b08b34a8d2f6b07d1d1eb003f4d3cf95f9db77c","tid":30063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"創世紀18章20-21節： <br />\n<br />\n20.耶和華說：所多瑪和蛾摩拉的罪惡甚重，聲聞於我。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n創世紀19章24-28節： <br />\n<br />\n24.當時，耶和華將硫磺與火從天上耶和華那裡降與所多瑪和蛾摩拉，  <br />\n25.把那些城和全平原，並城裏所有的居民，連地上生長的，都毀滅了。  <br />\n26.羅得的妻子在後邊回頭一看，就變成了一根鹽柱。  <br />\n27.亞伯拉罕清早起來，到了他從前站在耶和華面前的地方，  <br />\n28.向所多瑪和蛾摩拉與平原的全地觀看，不料，那地方煙氣上騰，如同燒碎一般。"},{"pid":"57a643588b6909c121a04d573a9d070d03e39c93","tid":30063,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/所多瑪與蛾摩拉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%89%80%E5%A4%9A%E7%91%AA%E8%88%87%E8%9B%BE%E6%91%A9%E6%8B%89&d=anOzd1FYTW2EZ%2B0L9%2Fb%2F9GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ca906ded\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/所多瑪與蛾摩拉</a>"},{"pid":"b1169b001beccda617466dee94678335ce812a1d","tid":30063,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zmb7o3nu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzmb7o3nu&h=b41ca48a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r20ca3ji\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr20ca3ji&h=7478397c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7YCdzozq98M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7YCdzozq98M&d=anOzd1FYTW2EZ%2B0L9%2Fb%2F9GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=33750561\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7YCdzozq98M</a>"},{"pid":"46856b1c8fe2bb85b1bdb472f62ed04c45923795","tid":30063,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上帝點解唔毀滅支那？</blockquote><br />\n因為上帝仲惡過支那"},{"pid":"bc8ef051010ef29ea79df9bbaddacd8984cc2dc4","tid":30063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上帝點解唔毀滅支那？</blockquote><br />\n因為上帝仲惡過支那</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9163a95639ae39f268d37c6f0a1cb648f246196a","tid":30063,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T00:43:42.000Z","msg":"因毛X東去左天堂帶領大量紅衛兵<br />\n挷住上帝來批鬥"},{"pid":"b1970ea180215f7ba1b878993fd8cf505e31036a","tid":30063,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上帝點解唔毀滅支那？</blockquote><br />\n因為上帝仲惡過支那</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係事實 起座塔又要搞鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}